	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Mario Kart-like game could be made with usual pseudo-3d road, actually - that way Street Racer (a Mario Kart clone) was made for <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1ntffRUHvPA" class="postlink">Sega Genesis</a>. On <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yx9U68HzZGo" class="postlink">SNES</a> it uses Mode7, and on <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CGdHD9G93dM" class="postlink">PSX and Saturn</a> it has polygonal 3D. So it looks very different on every system, but plays similarly.

		

		</td>
